## ✅ Fixed Issues (12 total)

ISSUE-001, 002, 003, 005, 006, 011, 017, 018, 019 + report card summary, teacher notices, admin fee UI alignment.

## 🚫 Intentionally NOT Fixed

| Issue | Why Not Fixed |
|---|---|
| **ISSUE-016** — Dual fee systems ([StudentFee](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/StudentFee.ts#11-31) vs [FeePayment](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/FeePayment.ts#13-33)) | Merging requires a data migration. Risk > benefit. Both systems serve different admin views. |
| **ISSUE-021** — Library model split (public library vs admin library) | Unifying [Library](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Library.ts#3-15) and [LibraryDocument](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/LibraryDocument.ts#3-18) models requires migration. Content is read-only for students — no user-visible breakage. |
| **ISSUE-019** backend enforcement | The backend [Documents](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/library.ts#10-31) API still accepts overdue submissions (correct — admin controls the due date, late submissions go to admin review). No backend change needed. |

